00:44:06.630 --> 00:44:07.130
Right?

00:44:07.130 --> 00:44:12.860
When I wake up in the morning,
when I pick up my toothbrush,

00:44:12.860 --> 00:44:16.070
the next thing that I do is I
pick up my tube of toothpaste.

00:44:16.070 --> 00:44:17.990
And I put the toothpaste
